title.narrative: Safe Wash II

description.narrative: (Nepal): With FY 2015 funds, USAID will improve sanitation status and hygiene behavior, enhance access for and quality of drinking water and improve local governance and maintenance of WASH facilities. This project will generally focus on district Open Defecation Free (ODF) in three districts (Kailali, Kanchanpur, Darchula) and promoting post ODF activities in Accham which has already been declared as ODF. Furthermore, this project will also aim to reach underserved populations with access to improved water supply services.
